Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大闹扎拉姆的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胆子不小啊 孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 老大说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:03:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是因为UE出现才去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE 外星人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你这个大战外星人的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是何方来客
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大摇大摆开着机动战士出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我手下的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如你所见 年纪尚小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也常为他伤透了脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古…古鲁迪克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么古鲁迪克先生会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 他们凭什么抓走菲利特啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那条街是扎拉姆的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放着外来者不管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被敌对的艾乌巴瞧不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地盘之争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的联邦军是干什么吃的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎拉姆和艾乌巴之间的摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军一向视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是这里的潜规则
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎拉姆和艾乌巴什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和菲利特有什么关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷 把拖车开过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去要回菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开军用车去就闹大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算了 我一个人去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在同一座卫星里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却动用机动战士打仗的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷不担心菲利特的安全吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座卫星太奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要找回菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 拖车着实不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就用我的卡车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就停在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定比跑着去要快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊瓦克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 坐下吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是卫星上少见的天然食材
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错过这村就没这店了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 老大说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身份不是明确了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我回船上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚逮住就马上放人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被艾乌巴的人瞧不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 稍安勿躁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有空在乎那些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE不知什么时候又会来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真到那时候再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说下次遇袭的可能是艾乌巴的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争不是早就结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何必没完没了 至今还这么敌视？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他们还自称艾乌巴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就必须为扎拉姆而战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这… 完全无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们祖祖辈辈为扎拉姆而战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比这更崇高和有尊严的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 老大说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子 那台叫高达的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让给我如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们扎拉姆引以为豪的高性能机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉拉一拥而上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也费了好大的功夫才制服它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那么大的能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能轻易干翻艾乌巴的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想用高达…做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 加上高达的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战舰的事可以细谈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战舰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们提供的条件已经足够
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就在战舰之外另加金额
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要多少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达不会给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用高达
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继承死去母亲的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁扎先生的遗志！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因UE失去双亲的孩子和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去妻儿的舰长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才说我们纠缠于过去的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不也是和过去纠缠不清的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 不会有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看他那样 小家伙可精明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在享受大餐也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也讨厌整天打架的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和姐姐想的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这不是莉莉亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪儿啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 正准备去和扎拉姆讲理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思 也带上我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对扎拉姆和艾乌巴有得是话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 莉莉亚 有好玩的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 带上他们好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么好不好 没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么稍安勿躁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和软禁有什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战舰是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了UE的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为摧毁它 需要战斗力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE的巢穴？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们的根据地？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摧毁那里的话 这场战争就会结束吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 为什么非要从这里买战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告联邦军总司令部的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更大的舰队也不成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手是UE 岂能指望如今的联邦军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军如果真有作战能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺拉也不会被毁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的双亲也不至会死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去妻儿的舰长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克先生被UE夺走了家人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我是同志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起来吧 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达的机师是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:11:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而能够对它进行最佳指挥的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交出菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特没有任何错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即放了他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法丁不是扎拉姆和艾乌巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少拽了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向我爸爸道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不允许欺负我的好爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.13,0:11:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有莉莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一车孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何处置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让吉拉出去吓跑他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没空陪孩子玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 孩子的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾乌巴那群杂种…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天的胜负还没分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我勒克特·艾法梅尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为高贵的艾乌巴骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶爱机艾美达前来拜访！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对面专程前来拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让客人空手回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 老大说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老夫的机动战士迦拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 随时可以出动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:13:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,院里的机动战士怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顾不上那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先放在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾乌巴的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些孩子在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勒克特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷 这里危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子 快上车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腿软了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉 没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里离城区远
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上孩子们先回歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.62,0:14:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些孩子 和扎拉姆艾 乌巴根本无关
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉拉不堪一击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在高贵的艾美达面前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然只有一败涂地啊 扎拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以扎拉姆之名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是不败的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更不会谄媚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾乌巴的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想为昨天做个了结是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我冬波老爹 亲自做你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 老年人请自重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以高贵的艾乌巴之名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以艾乌巴之名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎拉姆是宇宙最强！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 老大说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了搞偷袭一无是处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货 让你嚣张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 为什么要打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的战争也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天打架今天还惦记着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太不男人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为进行着这样的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会连累无辜的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也是为以前的事打打杀杀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.85,0:16:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那台高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想否认！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把菲利特跟你们混为一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个外人知道什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不想知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些让人们不幸的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎拉姆和艾乌巴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不都是在一个卫星上生活的伙伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE的机动战士型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一台离开编队了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 古鲁迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一台冲我们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是古鲁迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在郊外发现一台UE机动战士型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待命中的杰诺亚斯立即出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 这里也需要高达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么 别碍事 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 轮不到小孩出场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡是砸我们地盘的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论艾乌巴还是UE都一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们扎拉姆自己对付
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 老大说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE之类艾乌巴足以应付
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取下它们的首级扬名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以艾乌巴之名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎拉姆 艾乌巴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎拉姆 艾乌巴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要坚持到艾米莉她们逃进宇宙港
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见了 是宇宙港的升降机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是拉甘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢不了这家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 活着吗 回话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉甘？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特回歌姬号上去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说AGE系统造出了了不得的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE系统 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以对抗那台机动战士的新式武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯已经在准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去
